/* ============================================================
   TRAJECTORY — bundled build (single classic script, no ES
   modules). Generated by concatenating data.js, core.js,
   dashboard.js, profile.js, and app.js in dependency order, then
   stripping import/export statements (everything shares one script
   scope instead). This exists so the app works when index.html is
   opened directly via file:// — browsers block ES module imports
   (CORS) under file://, which silently breaks every button with no
   visible error. The source-of-truth files are still data.js /
   core.js / dashboard.js / profile.js / app.js; if you edit those,
   regenerate this bundle rather than editing it directly.
   ============================================================ */


